---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AffiliateLink from '../components/AffiliateLink.astro';

const meta = {
  title: 'How to Choose an AI Website Builder: Decision Framework (2025)',
  description: 'Most people pick the wrong AI website builder. Here\'s the decision framework that saves you from rebuilding your site in 3 months.',
  image: '/og-image.svg',
  keywords: ['choose AI website builder', 'AI website builder comparison', 'how to pick website builder', 'AI website generator guide'],
};
---

<Layout {...meta}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-[#FEF9F3] py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-black text-[#E07A5F] mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">
        Decision Framework Â· Stop Rebuilding Sites
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
        How to Choose an AI Website Builder
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Most people pick AI website builders like they pick restaurants â€” looks good from outside, regret the meal. Here's how to pick the right tool the first time.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-[#E07A5F]/10 border-2 border-[#E07A5F] rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Quick answer: You're answering the wrong question. Don't ask "Which AI builder is best?" Ask "What does my site ACTUALLY need?"
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Wrong Question -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      You're Asking the Wrong Question
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 my-8">
      <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Wrong question: "Which AI website builder is best?"</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">This assumes there's a universal winner. There isn't. Durable crushes for landing pages. Framer crushes for blogs. v0.dev crushes for custom designs.</p>

      <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Right question: "What does my site actually need?"</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Start with what you're building. Match the tool to the job. Not the other way around.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Decision Framework -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      The Decision Framework
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- Question 1 -->
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-4">Question 1: What are you building?</h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">Single landing page?</p>
            <p>You need copy-first. Durable.co wins here. The AI writes actual marketing copy, not filler text.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">Design-heavy portfolio?</p>
            <p>You need visual polish. v0.dev creates the most beautiful AI-generated sites. Clean, modern, impressive.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">Multi-page site with blog?</p>
            <p>You need a CMS. Framer has built-in blogging, SEO, hosting. It's a platform, not just a builder.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Question 2 -->
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-4">Question 2: Do you know how to code?</h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">No coding skills?</p>
            <p>Durable.co and Framer are visual editors. You click, drag, edit. No code required.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">Comfortable with code?</p>
            <p>v0.dev exports clean React code. You can customize beyond the AI generation. Best control.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Question 3 -->
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-4">Question 3: What's your budget?</h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">$0-15/month?</p>
            <p>All three have free tiers. v0.dev has the most generous free plan (100 generations/month).</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">$15-30/month?</p>
            <p>You can use any paid tier. Framer and Durable are around $15/mo. v0.dev is $20/mo.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">Money matters less than quality?</p>
            <p>Pay for the tool that matches your use case. Saving $10/month isn't worth rebuilding in 3 months.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Question 4 -->
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-orange-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-4">Question 4: Will you export the code?</h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">Yes, I want to host elsewhere?</p>
            <p>v0.dev is the only one that exports clean, production-ready code. Durable and Framer are hosted platforms.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-bold mb-2">No, I want them to host it?</p>
            <p>Durable and Framer include hosting. SSL, CDN, updates handled. Less to manage.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Decision Matrix -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Quick Reference: Which Tool for Your Use Case?
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-100">
            <th class="p-4 border font-bold">Use Case</th>
            <th class="p-4 border font-bold">Best Tool</th>
            <th class="p-4 border font-bold">Why</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 border">Landing page with great copy</td>
            <td class="p-4 border"><strong>Durable.co</strong></td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Best AI writing for marketing</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 border">Portfolio / design showcase</td>
            <td class="p-4 border"><strong>v0.dev</strong></td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Most beautiful designs</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 border">Blog + marketing site</td>
            <td class="p-4 border"><strong>Framer</strong></td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Built-in CMS and SEO</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 border">Developer who wants code control</td>
            <td class="p-4 border"><strong>v0.dev</strong></td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Exports clean React</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 border">Non-technical user</td>
            <td class="p-4 border"><strong>Durable.co</strong></td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Easiest to use</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 border">Agency building client sites</td>
            <td class="p-4 border"><strong>Framer</strong></td>
            <td class="p-4 border">Professional platform</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Common Mistakes -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Common Mistakes (Don't Do These)
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black mb-3">ðŸš¨ Mistake 1: Picking the "most popular" tool</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Popularity doesn't mean it's right for you. Framer is popular, but if you need a single landing page with great copy, Durable is better.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black mb-3">ðŸš¨ Mistake 2: Choosing by price alone</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Saving $5/month isn't worth rebuilding your site in 3 months when you realize the tool doesn't fit your needs. Match features first, price second.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black mb-3">ðŸš¨ Mistake 3: Not testing the free tier first</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">All three tools have free tiers. Use them. Build a test page. See if you like the interface. THEN pay.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black mb-3">ðŸš¨ Mistake 4: Ignoring export limitations</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">If you think you'll want to move to custom hosting later, v0.dev is your only real option. Durable and Framer are hosted platforms.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black mb-3">ðŸš¨ Mistake 5: Assuming AI = instant perfect site</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">AI gets you 80% there. You still need to edit, refine, customize. Plan for that time investment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Reviews -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-6 text-gray-900">
      Full Tool Reviews
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href="/durable-co-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Durable.co Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">3-week test results.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/v0-dev-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">v0.dev Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">3-week test results.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/framer-ai-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Framer Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">2-week test results.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
